<plot>Using two separate filmmaking teams (an all-white crew filming white residents and an all-black camera crew filming black residents), Two Towns of Jasper captures very different racial views by townsfolk in Jasper, Texas, the location for a racially motivated murder of an African American in 1998.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?622870</url></doc>
